Set the proper font size:
$ vim /etc/lightdm/lightdm-gtk-greeter.conf
Add the following line under "[greeter]":
xft-dpi=120

Set the DPI on the Xserver:
$ vim /etc/lightdm/lightdm.conf
Under the following section "[Seat:*]" have the following line:
xserver-command=X -dpi 120

Note:
This resource is very informative:
https://linuxreviews.org/HOWTO_set_DPI_in_Xorg
